ue to stale `AGENTS.md` — wants documentation for new modules in `src/lib/` (agent-dispatch.ts, agent-resolver.ts, session-manager.ts, trace-id.ts). Documentation debt, not a story 4-3 issue.\n- Build, tests (36/36), and coverage (100% trace-id.ts) all clean.\n- All 9 ACs verified with evidence.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 2, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: test:unit run (~50 lines), trace-id verbose test (~40 lines), coverage (~20 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: codeharness verify called twice\n\n### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — create-story (2026-04-03T01:05)\n\n- **Risk:** AC #4 depends on `templates/agents/evaluator.yaml` having `disallowedTools: [Edit, Write]` from story 3-2. Not verified that template exists.\n- `/tmp/` path pattern is Unix-specific. Not a concern on darwin but noted for portability.\n- All 9 ACs are test-provable (pure file system operations testable with real temp dirs).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Read: 7, Grep: 3, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads (architecture-v2.md: 2 reads)\n- Redundant operations: Two Grep calls to `source_access` could have been one\n\n### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — dev-story (2026-04-03T01:10)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- By tool: Read: 5, Bash: 4, Grep: 4, Write: 2, Edit: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: coverage run (~160 lines), full test suite (~20 lines), tsc noEmit (~20 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — code-review (2026-04-03T01:18)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- HIGH: Path traversal via runId injection — unsanitized user input in file path. Fixed with `sanitizeRunId()`.\n- HIGH: Silent file overwrite on basename collision — data loss. Fixed with `deduplicateFilename()`.\n- MEDIUM: Stale workspace contamination from crashed runs. Fixed with pre-