{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DYt879p72ZVuzWswZMGkjK","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 10 ACs verified. Here is the final report.\n\n---\n\n## Verification Results: Story 5-2 — Flow Execution Loop Blocks\n\n**Final Result: ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs)**\n\n### Step 1: Build\n**PASS** — `npm run build` succeeded. Output: ESM build + DTS build completed without errors.\n\n### Step 2: Tests\n**PASS** — 3992 passed, 0 failed across 155 test files. 68 workflow-engine tests (39 existing + 29 new loop block tests).\n\n### Step 3: Lint\n**PASS** — 0 errors, 50 warnings (all pre-existing, none in workflow-engine.ts).\n\n### Step 4: Coverage (workflow-engine.ts)\n- Statements: 96.37%\n- Branches: 88.75%\n- Functions: 100%\n- Lines: 97.86%\n\nAll exceed the 80% threshold required by AC #9.\n\n### Step 5: Per-AC Verification\n\n| AC | Description | Result | Evidence |\n|----|-------------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Loop block processing replaces skip | PASS | `executeLoopBlock()` exported; test \"executes loop blocks instead of skipping them\" |\n| 2 | Loop terminates on pass verdict | PASS | Test \"terminates loop when verdict is pass (AC #2)\" |\n| 3 | Loop terminates on maxIterations | PASS | `DEFAULT_MAX_ITERATIONS = 5`; test \"terminates loop when maxIterations reached (AC #3)\" |\n| 4 | Loop terminates on circuit breaker | PASS | Test \"terminates loop when circuit_breaker.triggered is true (AC #4)\" |\n| 5 | Finding injection + failed-story-only retry | PASS | `buildRetryPrompt()`, `getFailedItems()` exported; test \"injects findings into retry prompt for failed stories (AC #5)\" |\n| 6 | Verdict parsing from DispatchResult.output | PASS | `parseVerdict()` exported; 9 unit tests + 2 integration tests cover success/failure paths |\n| 7 | Iteration increment and persistence | PASS | Test \"increments iteration and persists each loop pass (AC #7)\" |\n| 8 | Halt errors terminate loop | PASS | Tests cover RATE_L